        <name>Dads Rock (Southmead) - 8 Week Group</name>
        <address>Greenway Centre, Doncaster Road, Southmead, Bristol, BS10 5PY - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Bristol<br>4. Location: Greenway Centre, Doncaster Road, Southmead, Bristol, BS10 5PY - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Early Years<br>8. Age: Under 2<br>9. Level: All ABilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Early Years, Free<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: February 28 @ 10:00 - 11:30<br>Free<br>If you are a Bristol City Council Resident, join Evolve Music’s Southmead Dads Rock group for dads or male caregivers and children under 2!<br><br>Unleash your child’s potential with music! Develop emotional control, language, math skills & creativity through play.<br><br>STARTS: Saturday 24th January 2026<br><br>ENDS: Saturday 28th March 2026<br><br>FREQUENCY: Weekly*, Saturday mornings 10am – 11.30am<br><br>VENUE: Greenway Centre, Doncaster Road, Southmead, Bristol, BS10 5PY<br><br>Discover how child-led musical play helps with developing baby and toddler’s managing big emotions, powerful communication skills, a love of language, a foundation in numbers and their inner rockstar.<br><br>Dads Rock (it’s not just a saying, it’s a movement!) is also a chance to build a community with other Dads and share your parenting adventure and musical experiences.<br><br>The group is an 8-week adventure and is absolutely free to join. It is made possible through Bristol Family Hubs and you will need to be a Bristol City Council resident to access sessions.<br><br>Southmead Dads Rock starts on 24th January and runs until the 28th March (there are no sessions taking place on 14th February or 14th March). Ideally Dads/male caregivers will join the musical revolution for the January start but this is not mandatory, so please do get in contact with us if you can only start after this date.<br><br>DATES: Session dates are Saturday mornings 10am – 11.30am<br><br>24th January<br>31st January<br>7th February<br>21st February<br>28th February<br>7th March<br>21st March<br>28th March<br>*Please note there are no sessions running on 14th February or 14th March.<br><br>BOOKING INFO: https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/southmead-dads-rock-8-week-group-january-2026-tickets-1978286666674?aff=oddtdtcreator<br><br>Contact Emma if you would like further information about the group before signing up – emma@evolvemusic.org.uk<br>14. When: Saturdays 10:00 - 11:30 (8 - week length) <br>(until 21st march)<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://evolvemusic.org.uk/whats-on/month/<br>16. Organisation Name: Evolve Music<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1637-FFD600-labelson</styleUrl>
