        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Berkshire<br>4. Location: Reading Music Centre, Reading - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Rock Band<br>7. Genre: Rock<br>8. Age: All Ages<br>9. Level: All Abilities (Electric Guitar, Bass Guitar, Keys, Drums, Singers)<br>10. Instruments: Guitar, Bass Guitar, Piano/Keys, Singing, Songwriting, Composing<br>11. Other Tags: Preparatory, Grade 1, Grade 2, Grade 3, Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: https://www.berksmusictrust.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Fees-2025-26-FINAL-EXT.pdf<br>13. About Opportunity: Soundstage is an electric band workshop where you'll learn to play a range of classic and current tracks from your favourite bands and artists, or even showcase your own song writing. Genres covered could be rock and pop, to video game music and beyond! Suitable for electric guitarists, bass guitarists, drummers, keys players and singers of all abilities.<br>14. When: Saturdays 13:00 - 14:00, 14:00 - 15:00<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.berksmusictrust.org.uk/music/music-groups/ensembles/<br>16. Organisation Name: Berkshire Music Trust<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.berksmusictrust.org.uk<br>19. Only for London/Local?: No Restriction<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
