          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>This ensemble is for young string players that have achieved Grade 1 to 3 standard meet to play together and consolidate their instrumental learning while having fun making music with other children of their same standard. Rehearsal time will focus on the development of basic musical skills such as rhythm and counting as well as the correct use of basic bowing techniques.</value>
          </Data>
