            <value><![CDATA[Out of the Attic is a friendly, inclusive orchestra for adults. Our name was given by our founding members, many of whom were returning to playing music after a long break and were getting their instruments back 'Out of the Attic'. This ensemble is suited to any string, brass, woodwind or percussion players of roughly grade 5 standard or above. We are always pleased to welcome new members so please do get in touch if you would like to join.]]></value>
