          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>During this activity pupils of Grade 6 to 8 meet weekly to work on well-established string repertoire, such as pieces for string orchestra, as well as solo concerts. This ensemble regularly takes part in “Music for Youth Festival” performing in famous venues around the country. Most of the pupils that attend this ensemble are also members of the Berkshire Youth Symphony Orchestra. This String ensemble includes a social break where all senior ensembles at Music Centre can meet.</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Saturdays 10:15 - 12:15</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
