          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>This is a great opportunity for those more established young string players that are currently working at Grade 3 to 5 standard. During this rehearsal pupils will have a first experience of pieces that they will probably recognise from the standard orchestral repertoire. Sight-reading skills will be practised regularly and new bowing techniques will be introduced, such as those off the string articulations.</value>
