          <Data name="11. Other Tags">
            <value>Grade 8</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>https://www.berksmusictrust.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Fees-2025-26-FINAL-EXT.pdf</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Berkshire Youth Saxophone Ensemble exists to join together the county's most talented young saxophonists in order to inspire and challenge them, and to develop their ability to perform chamber music to a high level. The group aims to explore a wide range of repertoire with influence from both western classical music and the world of jazz and there are often opportunities to explore improvisation. Pupils are also given the chance to play on the auxiliary instruments such as the soprano or baritone saxophone. Alongside tuition from our saxophone specialist teachers we have previously also worked with top level professional players including Rob Buckland and Gerard McChrystal.]]></value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Fridays 18:00 - 18:45</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
