          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>Free</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Launched in 2023 in a partnership with Youthsayers the free Jazz Reggae Afrobeat course encouraged young musicians to develop their live music playing alongside professionals. 

In 2024 The Jazzrobeat Collective was created by the dedicated group with support from CultureMix tutors Jamie and Ruel for live performances at Carnival of the World and Readipop Festival.

To join the 2026 Summer course you will have some experience of playing a musical instrument so you can improve by playing in a band. The focus is on Afro Jazz, Funk and Reggae genres to develop and build up your music skills.

You are required to bring your own instruments like horns or guitars. CultureMix Arts has limited instruments available including keyboards and drum kit.

Classes are during term time only and you can book anytime.

For more information contact CultureMix Arts. Office: 0118 9587351 Mobile: 07973 251919

What to expect:
During the course you will learn, develop and rehearse new songs with the group for a performance at the end. Watch the above video and read about the Summer short course here.

The course takes place during term time. Please take careful note of the session dates.</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Mondays 17:30 - 19:00 </value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
            <value>https://culturemixarts.co.uk/education/workshops-2/jazzrobeat-collective-afro-jazz-funk-music-making-course-for-12-18s-2/</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="16. Organisation Name">
            <value>CultureMix</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="17. About Organisation">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="18. Organisation Website">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="19. Only for London/Local?">
            <value>No Restriction</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="20. Extra Notes">
            <value>Limited to 16 places - signup/pre-booking required</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
