          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Join our dynamic ensemble, Sax is our Business, dedicated to intermediate and advanced saxophone players in Truro! Be part of a vibrant group where you'll fine-tune your skills, collaborate with like-minded musicians, and explore an exciting repertoire. From thrilling performances to diverse gigs throughout the year, this is your chance to elevate your saxophone prowess while having a blast making music together. Don't miss the chance to be part of this fantastic saxophone ensemble!
Musical Director - Steve Clifford

Steve studied clarinet under Colin Courtney in London and on leaving college joined the Royal Air Force as a musician. He was posted to the RAF Central Band and performed with them for 26 years. During his military career, he performed with the RAF Central Band, The RAF Squadronaires and the RAF Dance Orchestra, touring and performing throughout the world including USA, Japan, Africa and Europe.

On retiring to Cornwall, he joined CMST and acts as the cross service lead for first access. Teaching in schools and colleges from Truro through to Saltash.

 Want to join the sensational Sax is our Business? Shoot us an email to find out more!]]></value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Mondays 19:00 - 20:15</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
