            <value>The Devon Youth Saxophone Ensemble is a new county-wide group for young saxophonists around Grade 4 and above. It offers the chance to develop ensemble skills, play fun and varied repertoire, and meet like-minded musicians. Starting on 16th November, the ensemble will explore chamber music for small and medium saxophone groups across six Gathering Days throughout the year, each running from 2:00–4:30pm.</value>
