          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Small groups for children who enjoy music and singing. Excellent preparation for learning an instrument as well as complementary
to those who already are. Progressive classes based on the Hungarian pedagogy of Zoltan Kodály, run by Rebecca Willson, Devon's Regional Coordinator for the
British Kodály Academy.

Suitable for children already learning instruments above grade 3 who want to improve sight reading and aural skills. Learning through singing
but also incorporates instruments where appropriate. £8]]></value>
