      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Exeter Children's Orchestra]]></name>
        <address>Woodwater Lane Academy, Exeter - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Devon<br>4. Location: Woodwater Lane Academy, Exeter - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Orchestra<br>7. Genre: Orchestral<br>8. Age: 7 - 18<br>9. Level: Learning an orchestral instrument & be able to read music<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Preparatory, Grade 1, Grade 2, Grade 3, Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: £50 per term<br>13. About Opportunity: Exeter Children's Orchestra offers children and young people aged 7-18 (and their families) the chance to play a wide variety of music in a fun, friendly and safe environment.<br><br>New members are always welcome and there are no scary auditions!  ​<br><br>Exeter Children's Orchestra is a charity registered in England (no.801384). The orchestra is run by a committee of volunteers - all parents of orchestra members - who make sure that the orchestra is a fun and safe place for children to make music.<br> <br>Parents who wish to play too are DBS checked. And are most welcome to join this unique orchestra. <br><br>The orchestra puts on at least 3 concerts a year and also makes special guest appearances at music festivals such as the Teignmouth Classical Music Festival and the Devon Mix<br><br>In 2020 we opened our doors to Junior Members - Those who were learning an instrument but were not ready to join in with the main orchestra.<br>In 2025 we exapnded on this to include those who are brand new to their intruments and just at the very start of their musical journey. <br><br>It's not all music making though. We also try to have an annual social event for the children and parents as well as efforts to start overseas trips post-COVID.<br>14. When: Saturdays 10:00 - 12:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.exeterchildrensorchestra.co.uk<br>16. Organisation Name: Exeter Children's Orchestra<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.exeterchildrensorchestra.co.uk<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
