          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>This is our Twenty-eight-week programme to learn an instrument from scratch in a group. It is open to all secondary school students from years 7 to 13. Instruments are provided free of charge to use at Music Centre, and can be rented to take home for a small fee. We offer certain rare orchestral instruments in Kick-Start:
TROMBONE, TUBA, VIOLIN, CLARINET, CELLO, DOUBLE BASS, PERCUSSION</value>
          </Data>
