          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Plymouth Youth Symphony Orchestra started in October 2022 for musicians aged between 11 and 21.  We are offering young musicians of intermediate and advanced ability (of grade 4 and above or equivalent), the opportunity to play exciting, challenging and varied orchestral works from symphonies to overtures and musicals to film music. 
​
Strings: Violin, Viola, Cello & Double Bass
Woodwind: Oboe, Flute, Clarinet, Bassoon
Brass: Trumpet, French Horn, Trombone, Tuba
Percussion: Drum Kit, Timpani, Tuned
​
As with all our ensembles it is free to join and to participate
Weekly rehearsals each Wednesday 5:30pm - 7:00pm at Marjon University

For more information contact pysorchestra@gmail.com or use the “Contact Us” form on this website.]]></value>
