          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>
Special Voices Choir
Plymouth Special Voices Choir, is a free, fully inclusive choir. It is open to any Plymouth child (5-19) with an Education Health Care Plan (EHCP).
​
The Choir started in September 2023 and is based at Woodlands Special School (PL6 5ES) on a Tuesday evening, 4:30-5:30.
​
Run and Directed by our SEND Music Lead – Stuart Penman.
​
For more information contact: spenman@woodlands.plymouth.sch.uk</value>
