          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Plymouth Youth Steel is a steel pans band that has just been relaunched after a gap of a couple of years.
 
Rehearsals are at Marine Academy Plymouth on Thursdays, 6pm -7pm during term time. The band meets in the theatre and is mainly aimed at Key stage 3 and Key stage 4 players.
 
The band is led by Rachael Duchnovski, a top steel band player who has performed regularly at national events including the Notting Hill Carnival and the Albert Hall.
​
New players are always welcome! 
 
Contact us:  youthmusic@plymouth.gov.uk</value>
          </Data>
