          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>
 
All flautists welcome from Grade 1 to Grade 8+.
 
We play a wide variety of music, including film and show tunes and current repertoire includes Mozart, Scott Joplin and an experimental piece for headjoints only!
Some pieces have alto, bass and piccolo parts and alto and bass flutes are available at the centre to have a go at.
 
New members are always welcome so why not come along and enjoy meeting other flautists whilst learning new music to perform at our concerts?

Instruments: Flutes
 
Standard: Grade 1 upwards
 
Led by: Catherine Nicholls
</value>
