        <name>NDMC - Guitar Ensemble</name>
        <address>Pilton Community College, Barnstaple - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Devon<br>4. Location: Pilton Community College, Barnstaple - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Guitar Group<br>7. Genre: Classical<br>8. Age: All aged children<br>9. Level: Grade 1+<br>10. Instruments: Guitar<br>11. Other Tags: Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: from £46 per term<br>13. About Opportunity: <br> <br>There are currently over 20 guitarists in our ensemble ranging from grade 1 to grade 8. We enjoy working together to create our very own unique sound and to perform various styles of music including baroque, classical, Spanish, Latin American and film music. We also perform wonderful modern pieces especially written for guitar ensemble by British composers.<br> <br>We are always very pleased to welcome classical and acoustic guitarists of grade 1 standard and above. The parts are arranged to suit the ability of the guitarists to enable them to be involved in producing our musical performances. Our rehearsals are fun and very relaxed, everyone is made to feel welcome!<br> <br> <br>Standard:  Grade 1 to Grade 8+<br> <br>Led by: Hannah Johnson<br>14. When: Wednesdays 18:00 - 19:00<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.northdevonmusiccentre.co.uk/groups/<br>16. Organisation Name: North Devon Music Centre<br>17. About Organisation: The North Devon Music Centre is a non profit organisation that helps young (and young at heart) people who are learning to play an instrument to enjoy making music together through ensemble playing.<br> <br>Learning to play together not only requires new skills to those learnt as a solo player, but also provides the opportunity to make new friends, experience music in a whole new way and helps in becoming a better all-round musician.<br> <br>We meet weekly through school term time and hold regular concerts where we showcase to family, friends and other music lovers. We are made up of 8 different groups of players, led by experienced musicians, catering for all levels, all ages and all types of instruments!<br> <br>Please have a look around our site to find out more, or contact us today.<br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.northdevonmusiccentre.co.uk<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
