            <value>
 
There are currently over 20 guitarists in our ensemble ranging from grade 1 to grade 8. We enjoy working together to create our very own unique sound and to perform various styles of music including baroque, classical, Spanish, Latin American and film music. We also perform wonderful modern pieces especially written for guitar ensemble by British composers.
 
We are always very pleased to welcome classical and acoustic guitarists of grade 1 standard and above. The parts are arranged to suit the ability of the guitarists to enable them to be involved in producing our musical performances. Our rehearsals are fun and very relaxed, everyone is made to feel welcome!
 
 
Standard:  Grade 1 to Grade 8+
 
Led by: Hannah Johnson</value>
