          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>
RootNotes Community Singing Circle
A new monthly singing group for voices of all ages led by Natural Voice Practitioner Lara Conley
Find your voice and enjoy singing together - no experience needed - just a love of singing!
​
First Monday of the month, 4-5pm
Alwington Village Hall, Fairy Cross, near Bideford, EX39 5AW
​
Adults: £5 / Children: £2.50 (under 5s free)
*please note that children must be accompanied by a participating adult
​
Please email/message Becki Driscoll for more info or to book -
becki@rootnotes.org.uk / 07811 279230</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>First monday of the month, 16:00 - 17:00</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
            <value>https://www.rootnotes.org.uk/community-singing-circle</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="16. Organisation Name">
            <value>RootNotes</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="17. About Organisation">
            <value><![CDATA[
Welcome to the RootNotes website!
​
RootNotes is a Bideford-based community music organisation, run by local musician Becki Driscoll.
​
RootNotes offers music workshops for all ages and all abilities in a variety of different settings. Whether you are a confident player or just starting out on your musical journey RootNotes offers opportunities to join in and and take part.
​
Our weekly music groups encourage people to have fun whilst learning music and song, with an emphasis on 'hands-on' learning. We can provide instruments for sessions, or help you to develop skills on your own instrument within the group.
Becki Driscoll Community Musician
Young performers with RootNotes
RootNotes music workshops are suitable for schools, preschools, SEN settings, care homes and community events. Workshops can be tailored to suit a theme or a specific group of people.
​
If you are interested in coming along to one of the music groups or would like to book a RootNotes music workshop for your setting please get in touch!
​​]]></value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="18. Organisation Website">
            <value>https://www.rootnotes.org.uk</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="19. Only for London/Local?">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="20. Extra Notes">
            <value/>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
