          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[A daytime group for adults interested in playing and singing music in a gentle, informal way! Find your voice, enjoy singing together, have a go at playing an instrument and be part of the band.

Instruments can be provided for the sessions but you are also welcome to bring your own.
​
RootNotes Open House runs on Friday mornings at Alwington Village Hall, Fairy Cross, near Bideford. The session runs from 11am - 12.15. Please email becki@rootnotes.org.uk to check dates.
This group runs as a 'pay what you can afford' group with a suggested donation of £5 - £10 per session.
​]]></value>
