We have successfully held performances for Cats Protection, Ottery St Mary; Dalwood Coffee and Christmas Concerts;  Kings Manor, Ottery St Mary; Green Tree Court, Pinhoe: Sundial Care Home, Tipton St. John; Exmouth Stroke Club; Seaton Care Home; Vale View Care Home, Sidford; Churchill Homes Lockyer Lodge, Newton Poppleford Primary School and Ikea Exeter store all from whom we have received warm and appreciative feedback.  

We warmly welcome new and lapsed brass and percussion players so if you are interested in joining us, and would like any further information about the Band or for booking enquiries please complete the ‘contact us’ form on this site.

Band rehearsals are held on Wednesdays ​from 10.15 a.m. to 12.15 pm ​in our band room at Sidmouth Rugby Football Club Pavilion, Byes Lane, Sidford, EX10 9PY. There is a player contribution of £10 per month.]]></value>
