          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Adventurers; musical play group for d/Deaf or Visually Impaired preschoolers is our musical session for deaf or VI children and their parents/caregivers

Our interactive sessions are designed to support children’s development in areas such as communication, language and creativity; exploring musical sensory play in a safe and fun environment alongside other families.

Working in partnership with Plymouth City Council, Deaf Choices UK and local Teachers of the Deaf, we will join together with families each week to celebrate children’s uniqueness within an enabling and supportive creative space.

This is a closed session, but if you would like any more information about our work in Devon, please contact

beth@evolvemusic.org.uk</value>
          </Data>
