      <Placemark>
        <name>Dads Rock (Barton Hill) - 8 Week Group</name>
        <address>43 Ducie Rd, Barton Hill, Bristol BS5 0AX - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Devon<br>4. Location: 43 Ducie Rd, Barton Hill, Bristol BS5 0AX - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Early Years<br>8. Age: Under 2<br>9. Level: All ABilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Early Years, Free<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: If you are a Bristol City Council Resident, join Evolve Music’s Barton Hill Dads Rock group for dads or male caregivers and children under 2!<br><br>Unleash your child’s potential with music! Develop emotional control, language, math skills & creativity through play.<br><br>STARTS: Saturday 17th January 2026<br><br>ENDS: Saturday 21st March 2026<br><br>FREQUENCY: Weekly, Saturday mornings 10am – 11.30am<br><br>VENUE: The Swannery @ Wellspring Settlement, 43 Ducie Rd, Barton Hill, Bristol BS5 0AX<br><br>Discover how child-led musical play helps with developing baby and toddler’s managing big emotions, powerful communication skills, a love of language, a foundation in numbers and their inner rockstar.<br><br>Dads Rock (it’s not just a saying, it’s a movement!) is also a chance to build a community with other Dads and share your parenting adventure and musical experiences.<br><br>The group is an 8-week adventure and is absolutely free to join. It is made possible through Bristol Family Hubs and you will need to be a Bristol City Council resident to access sessions.<br><br>Barton Hill Dads Rock starts on 17th January 2026 and runs until the 21st March (there are no sessions taking place on 14th or 21st February due to half term). Ideally Dads / male caregivers will join the musical revolution for the January start but this is not mandatory, so please do get in contact with us if you can only start after this date.<br><br>DATES: Session dates are Saturday mornings 10am – 11.30am<br><br>17th January<br>24th January<br>31st January<br>7th February<br>28th February<br>7th March<br>14th March<br>21st March<br>*Please note there are no sessions running on 14th or 21st February.<br><br>BOOKING INFO: https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/barton-hill-dads-rock-8-week-group-january-2026-tickets-1978355874677?aff=oddtdtcreator<br><br>Contact Emma if you would like further information about the group before signing up – emma@evolvemusic.org.uk<br>14. When: Saturdays 10:00 - 11:30 (8 - week length) <br>(until 21st march)<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://evolvemusic.org.uk/whats-on/month/<br>16. Organisation Name: Evolve Music<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: Bristol City Residents]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1637-FFD600-labelson</styleUrl>
