        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Devon<br>4. Location: Devon - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: <br>8. Age: 14+<br>9. Level: All ABilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Free, SEND<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: Get creative from home with Sound Lab Online!<br><br>We invite young people (aged 14+) with ASC or additional learning needs to connect and collaborate through our free, fun, and social online music programme! Over the course of 1-hour sessions, we’ll guide you through composition skills, music production techniques, and interactive musical games. You will need access to a screen camera and a Zoom account. Boost your skills and make some noise with us at Sound Lab Online!<br><br>Get in contact with mark@evolvemusic.org.uk if you would like to try or join this group and we will complete an inclusion form with you to make sure you can get the most out of these sessions.<br>14. When: Fridays 17:45 - 18:15 (ONLINE) - check for exact dates<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://evolvemusic.org.uk/whats-on/month/<br>16. Organisation Name: Evolve Music<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
