          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Get creative from home with Sound Lab Online!

We invite young people (aged 14+) with ASC or additional learning needs to connect and collaborate through our free, fun, and social online music programme! Over the course of 1-hour sessions, we’ll guide you through composition skills, music production techniques, and interactive musical games. You will need access to a screen camera and a Zoom account. Boost your skills and make some noise with us at Sound Lab Online!

Get in contact with mark@evolvemusic.org.uk if you would like to try or join this group and we will complete an inclusion form with you to make sure you can get the most out of these sessions.</value>
