          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[
Young Carers
Our Young Carers music project takes places once or twice a month, on Mondays at Paignton Baptist Church on Winner Street. 
​
These sessions are open to all young people with a caring responsibility at home, whether they have undergone a formal Young Carers assessment or not.
​
Within these sessions, we are led by the group and their musical interests and ideas. Some weeks we create songs, jam, use our voices, experiment with instruments and music technology. Let us know what might interest you. 
​
To join these FREE sessions please email Laura on info@weneedmusic.org or call 07349904889. Alternatively, fill in this contact form and we'll get back to you.
​
Our upcoming dates for 2026 are:
Mon 23rd Feb
Mon 16th March
Mon 27th April
Mon 18th May
Mon 22nd June
Mon 29th June
We meet from 6.30-7.30pm at Paignton Baptist Church.]]></value>
          </Data>
