            <value><![CDATA[Aimed at key stage 1 children, young musicians are invited to gain musicianship development in this high quality session, set mainly around the piano learning fun songs and engaging rhythm games in an immensely fun setting with the inspiring professional music teacher, Jenny Barrett. They also develop aural & rhythmic skills towards instrumental learning. No previous experience is necessary. We involve a “try out an instrument” session each term.

