            <value><![CDATA[Following the continued success of our Poole Society of Young Musicians Wind Chamber music provision, we are pleased to be able to offer again this term the Senior Symphonic Wind ensemble for grade 4+ woodwind and brass players:  high quality coaching sessions with end performance with additional orchestral training this term.

This programme will take place this term over 4 Sunday afternoon sessions x  3 hours plus concert (free entry) and run by professional musician experts including Simon Gilliver & BSO Robb Tooley

Venue: Dumpton School, Wimborne. 
Training session dates: 25th Jan, 8th Feb, 1st March - Dumpton School 
8th March - Parkstone Grammar School with concert]]></value>
