        <name>BCP Youth Guitar Group</name>
        <address>Absolute Music, Bournemouth - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Dorset<br>4. Location: Absolute Music, Bournemouth - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Rock<br>8. Age: 7 - 16<br>9. Level: All Abilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: No Experience<br>12. Cost: £40 per year<br>13. About Opportunity: A fantastic opportunity to enjoy playing together and develop your guitar playing. Running on the first Saturday of every month at Absolute Music 10am -1:30pm during term time. <br><br>Open to all abilities of guitarist from year 3 to year 10. (Older students are very welcome as mentors, please email for me info.) Come join us to give it a try! Your first session is free to attend; however spaces are very limited so please email contact@chriswoodsgroove.co.uk now to book your space or get in touch to find out more.<br><br>In sessions we will be learning pieces, new techniques, jamming, composing and of course we will be working on pieces to perform.<br>14. When: First Saturday of the Month (10:00 - 13:30)<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://soundstorm-music.org.uk/schools-teachers/music-hub/ensembles/bcp-youth-guitar-group/<br>16. Organisation Name: Soundstorm Music<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
