          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>A fantastic opportunity to enjoy playing together and develop your guitar playing. Running on the first Saturday of every month at Absolute Music 10am -1:30pm during term time. 

Open to all abilities of guitarist from year 3 to year 10. (Older students are very welcome as mentors, please email for me info.) Come join us to give it a try! Your first session is free to attend; however spaces are very limited so please email contact@chriswoodsgroove.co.uk now to book your space or get in touch to find out more.

In sessions we will be learning pieces, new techniques, jamming, composing and of course we will be working on pieces to perform.</value>
