y a free taster session<br>New members are welcome to come along for a free taster session before signing up. It’s a great way to meet the group, try the session, and see if B Sharp Jams is the right fit.<br>14. When: Wednesdays 17:30 - 19:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://bsharp.org.uk/weekly-music/age-11-18/<br>16. Organisation Name: BSharp<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
