      <Placemark>
        <name>BSharp - Individual Sessions</name>
        <address>Dorset - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Dorset<br>4. Location: Dorset - UK<br>5. Type: Mentoring<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Various<br>8. Age: 8 - 25<br>9. Level: All Abilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Free<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: Individual sessions <br>We offer one-to-one music making sessions for young people age 8 – 25, who are experiencing challenging circumstances.  <br>For example, young people struggling with mental health issues, social isolation, low confidence or anxiety, and who would benefit from a safe, creative space to make music. <br>Sessions are led by professional music leaders and producers, and are built around what the young person is interested in and wants to do. <br>Please contact B Sharp for more information, or to refer a young person to this programme. Email info@bsharp.org.uk <br>14. When: Application Basis<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://bsharp.org.uk/take-part/music-to-support-wellbeing/<br>16. Organisation Name: BSharp<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
