          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Individual sessions 
We offer one-to-one music making sessions for young people age 8 – 25, who are experiencing challenging circumstances.  
For example, young people struggling with mental health issues, social isolation, low confidence or anxiety, and who would benefit from a safe, creative space to make music. 
Sessions are led by professional music leaders and producers, and are built around what the young person is interested in and wants to do. 
Please contact B Sharp for more information, or to refer a young person to this programme. Email info@bsharp.org.uk </value>
          </Data>
