          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Big Band is an opportunity for musicians grade 6+ to come together and make music. Students would have been learning their chosen instrument for years and be confident in playing in an ensemble. Time will be spent developing playing as a group with opportunity to perform exciting new repertoire throughout the year.  

Guitarists will need an understanding of reading standard notation/chord charts. Unfortunately, this ensemble is not suitable for tab readers only. Similarly, bassists will need to be proficient at reading standard notation, bass clef.</value>
