          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[This orchestra offers advanced string students an opportunity to rehearse and perform a wide range of works of the standard string orchestra and receive specialist coaching.

ACTIVITY OVERVIEW

This advanced String Orchestra provides students with opportunities to rehearse and perform standard String Orchestra repertoire. The tutors have many years of conducting and performing experience and encourage young musicians to develop lifelong skills playing music by composers such as Elgar, Tippett, Tchaikovsky, Shostakovich, Mozart, and Britten. HAYSO performs with The London Mozart Players, one of our organisation's Music Education Hub partners, during its annual series of concerts.

The orchestra recruits students learning an orchestral string instrument at Grade 5 level or above.]]></value>
