Junior String Orchestra is for string players who are Grades 1-2 and gives them their first experience of playing as full string orchestra, learning how to sight-read in a rehearsal and understanding the difference between playing the melody or an accompaniment part. They perform a wide variety of music from classical to film and popular style. There are also opportunities to try Viola and Double Bass!</value>
