          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>£91 per term</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[This is a fun group for those in year 3 and above, who are currently at a level of Grade 1 or above on their instrument.  

This group enables all woodwind (flute, clarinet, saxophone, oboe and bassoon), brass (trumpet, french horn, trombone, euphonium and tuba) and percussion students to experience playing in an ensemble and will prepare for performances at the centre.  

More advanced pupils are welcome to join and will gain experience before moving on to the Centre’s Jazz & Funk Band.  Come along and learn to play as an ensemble!]]></value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Saturdays 9:00 - 10:00</value>
          </Data>
