          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>A first ensemble for children who have just started to learn the Violin and Cello.

ENSEMBLE OVERVIEW

String Club is an opportunity for our youngest musicians to come together and start making music. Children will have been learning for at least 6 months and will be confident using the bow and their fingers. Time will be spent developing music reading skills, simple part-playing and general musicianship. A great way to help maintain enthusiasm in the early stages!</value>
