String group is for Violinists and Cellists who have been learning for over a year and are at a Pre-Grade 1 to Grade 1 level of learning. They will play tunes together as a mixed ensemble and learn how to follow a conductor. This fun ensemble will help the children to learn music of different styles and cultures, and assist them in developing their technique and general musicianship.</value>
