            <value>A chance to attend weekly sessions and complete the Grade V theory syllabus. 

ACTIVITY OVERVIEW

This course is perfect for those who have learnt the basics in theory and are now ready to sit their Grade V theory exam – something that is needed should you want to progress further than Grade 6 in you instrumental exams.

This course will springboard you ahead so you are ready to sit your grade V exam. The weekly classes will offer a combination of group teaching and personalised support to help you develop your knowledge of music theory and prepare you to take the new online version of the ABRSM theory exam.

Already part of Music Centre? There will be no additional fees for this course, Virtual Music Centre is free as part of your membership! </value>
