          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[An ideal ensemble for beginner woodwind & brass players who have been learning for at least a year and in year 4+

Why get involved?

Key Information

Apply for Woodwind Ensemble

Meet the Tutor
Other Music Centre Activities
ACTIVITY OVERVIEW

This ensemble is for all woodwind and brass instruments from grade 1 to grade 3 and are in year 4 or above. 

They will develop their ensemble skills playing fun music in a variety of styles and perform in concerts throughout the year. This is the ideal group for young musicians to gain ensemble playing experience before progressing into the more advanced youth concert band.]]></value>
