OBE, Guy Barker, Julian Bliss, Craig Mather, Band of the Bugles and the Rifles, Philip Harper, Andy Coxon, Nathanial Morrison, Keith Allan, Alexander L'Estrange, 5 Mics and Tom Davoran to name just a few! We also work with otherneighbouring Music Hubs such as South Gloucestershire and Bath and North East Somerset to collaborate on major projects such as the Music For Youth Massed Ensemble for the Schools Prom at the Royal Albert Hall!<br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.gloucestershiremusic.co.uk<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
