ut our past tours here<br>Partnership Working<br><br>At Gloucestershire Music we want to inspire our county’s musicians and young people and therefore we continue to work closely with National Partnership Organisations and professional ensembles and artists such as the Bournemouth Symphony Orchestra, National Choir of Great Britain, Birmingham Conservatoire (LEAP Ensemble), Tasmin Little OBE, Guy Barker, Julian Bliss, Craig Mather, Band of the Bugles and the Rifles, Philip Harper, Andy Coxon, Nathanial Morrison, Keith Allan, Alexander L'Estrange, 5 Mics and Tom Davoran to name just a few! We also work with otherneighbouring Music Hubs such as South Gloucestershire and Bath and North East Somerset to collaborate on major projects such as the Music For Youth Massed Ensemble for the Schools Prom at the Royal Albert Hall!<br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.gloucestershiremusic.co.uk<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
