        <name>Acoustic Band</name>
        <address>Oasis Academy Shirley Park, Croydon - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Oasis Academy Shirley Park, Croydon - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Mixed Ensemble<br>7. Genre: Other<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: <br>10. Instruments: Piccolo/Flute, Clarinet, Oboe, Cor Anglais, Bassoon, Violin, Viola, Cello, Double Bass, Harp, Guitar<br>11. Other Tags: <br>12. Cost: <br>13. About Opportunity: A group for acoustic guitars, strings, and woodwind. The repertoire is varied covering well-known pop to jazz and classical pieces. Whilst it helps to have good note reading skills, there are tab and chords parts provided. The group often shares projects with singers and other instrumental players and ensembles<br>14. When: Tuesdays 19:00 - 20:00<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.croydonmusicandarts.co.uk/learn-with-us/cma-centres-and-activities/weekly-timetable/<br>16. Organisation Name: Croydon Music Arts<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
