        <name>Concert Band</name>
        <address>Oasis Academy Shirley Park, Croydon - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Oasis Academy Shirley Park, Croydon - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Concert Band<br>7. Genre: Orchestral<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: Grade 2 - 5<br>10. Instruments: Piccolo/Flute, Clarinet, Oboe, Cor Anglais, Bassoon, Trumpet, Trombone, Tuba, Horns, Percussion, Piano/Keys<br>11. Other Tags: Grade 2, Grade 3, Grade 4, Grade 5<br>12. Cost: <br>13. About Opportunity: Recommended for wind and percussion players progressing from Star Workshop (Saturday 9am). Concert Band is for musicians of grade 2 - 5 standard, playing a wide variety of music including popular TV, film, and theatre themes as well as traditional concert band music and exciting collaborative and fusion works. Team spirit is a central part of Concert Band, which helps with our chemistry when performing together.<br>14. When: Saturdays 11:15 - 12:15<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.croydonmusicandarts.co.uk/learn-with-us/cma-centres-and-activities/friday-centre/<br>16. Organisation Name: Croydon Music Arts<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
