        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Oasis Academy Shirley Park, Croydon - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Orchestra<br>7. Genre: Orchestral<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: Grade 4-5+<br>10. Instruments: Piccolo/Flute, Clarinet, Oboe, Cor Anglais, Bassoon, Trumpet, Trombone, Tuba, Horns, Harp, Violin, Viola, Cello, Double Bass, Percussion, Euphonium<br>11. Other Tags: Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: <br>13. About Opportunity: CYCO performs music from a wide range of genres, from Baroque and Classical music to songs from musicals and film scores. Rehearsals focus on orchestral training and most students progress to the Youth Orchestra when appropriate. There is a fun and sociable atmosphere, espescially at break times. New members will be welcomed immediately by staff and their peers<br>14. When: Fridays 18:00 - 20:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.croydonmusicandarts.co.uk/learn-with-us/cma-centres-and-activities/friday-centre/<br>16. Organisation Name: Croydon Music Arts<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
