        <address>Bridge Academy, Laburnum Street, London - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Bridge Academy, Laburnum Street, London - UK<br>5. Type: Instrument Lessons<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Various<br>8. Age: 8 - 18<br>9. Level: Any level<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: <br>12. Cost: Depends on time<br>13. About Opportunity: In addition to our extensive work in schools supporting and enhancing curriculum music and in-school instrumental learning, Hackney Music Service offers a special programme of out-of-school instrumental tuition to children and young people across a 10-week term.<br><br>Tuition is offered in a range of instruments including: Woodwind, Piano and Guitar, other instruments may available depending on the demand.<br><br>If you do not have your own instrument, it may be possible to hire one directly from the music service where we have stock. Alternatively, please see our instrument purchase page for further advice.<br>14. When: Tuesdays, between 4.30pm – 7:30pm in time slots ranging from 20 minutes, 40 minutes, and 60 minutes.<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.hackneymusic.co.uk/activities/tuition/<br>16. Organisation Name: Hackney Music Service Network<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
