            <value>In addition to our extensive work in schools supporting and enhancing curriculum music and in-school instrumental learning, Hackney Music Service offers a special programme of out-of-school instrumental tuition to children and young people across a 10-week term.

Tuition is offered in a range of instruments including: Woodwind, Piano and Guitar, other instruments may available depending on the demand.

If you do not have your own instrument, it may be possible to hire one directly from the music service where we have stock. Alternatively, please see our instrument purchase page for further advice.</value>
