Trafalgar Square.<br><br>Hackney Training Orchestra is open to players in Year 4 and above<br>Applicants must be of Grade 2 standard or higher. Applicants need not necessarily have taken a Grade 2 exam but should be able to play and sight-read to the level expected for Grade 2 players<br>No audition is necessary for HTO. Players become members by recommendation from their instrumental tutor or school music teacher, or by applying directly to HMS<br>Applicants must either live in the borough of Hackney or attend a Hackney school<br>HTO may also accept pupils from neighbouring boroughs, please get in touch for more information<br>14. When: Tuesday 16:30 - 18:00<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.hackneymusic.co.uk/hackney-training-orchestra/<br>16. Organisation Name: Hackney Music Service Network<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
