          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>Free</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Do you want to be in a band, perform your favourite songs and write the hits of the future?

MEI offers weekly workshops for young people aged 13-18 to explore their passion for playing in bands and writing music.

Led by enthusiastic and highly experienced tutors, the sessions are fun and interactive. Whether you are just starting on an instrument or have played for some years, these weekly sessions will give you an opportunity to play or sing your favourite songs together with others. 

Who can join?


We’re looking for drummers, guitarists, bassists, pianists and singers of all levels. If you’re a string, woodwind or brass player, we would also love to hear from you.

No need to sign up, just come along!</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Tuesdays 16:00 - 18:00 (Highbury Roundhouse, Fridays 17:00 - 19:00 (Life Youth Hub)</value>
          </Data>
