          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Begin your child's musical journey
Our STARter Groups are the perfect first step. Designed especially for beginners, these fun, friendly group lessons give children the chance to learn an instrument, play together, and fall in love with making music. Ready to start your child's musical adventure?

What is a STARter Group?
No experience necessary: All children begin as complete beginners.
Group learning: Develop confidence, teamwork, and musical abilities in a collaborative setting.
Sing, play, perform: Singing is an integral part of every group's learning experience.
Concert culmination: Celebrate achievements with a special summer performance for parents and carers.]]></value>
