          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Jazz Jumpers is the perfect introduction to jazz for young instrumentalists of around Grade 1 to 3. The emphasis is on playing by ear, interacting and listening while playing together in a group, making up tunes, improvising together and having fun playing together.

JazzJumpers welcomes players of all instruments.

Rehearsals will take place in the Studio, led by Immy Churchill.

(NB After Jazz Jumpers, members move up to JazzWorks and then Merton Youth Jazz Orchestra)</value>
