            <value>Our Family Steps class is a mixed-age group for children under 5 and thJunior Repz Choir is for ages 8-12 (Years 4-7). These are fun sessions where children will learn a wide range of songs, develop vocal technique, get opportunities to perform, and meet others who love singing. This term the choir will be working towards writing their own original song to perform in Newham Festival of Stories in mid-Novembereir adults, offering playful opportunities for everyone to explore instruments and move their bodies, and to enjoy songs, rhymes and stories together</value>
