        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Redbridge, London - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Guitar Group<br>7. Genre: Orchestral<br>8. Age: Yr 3+<br>9. Level: Grade 1+<br>10. Instruments: Guitar<br>11. Other Tags: Grade 1, Grade 2, Grade 3, Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: https://visionrcl.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/RMS-Fees-Charges-September-2025.pdf<br>13. About Opportunity: RMS Guitar Club is open to guitar pupils of all styles and types, whether you read staff notation or TAB. Whether you play acoustic, classical, electric, bass or even ukulele, you will learn to perform effectively as a part of a group in a friendly and supportive environment. The repertoire is diverse and includes all major styles from classical through to jazz and rock.<br>14. When: Mondays 17:30 - 18:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://visionrcl.org.uk/music/learn-to-play/clubs/<br>16. Organisation Name: Redbridge Music Service<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
