        <name>Saturday BandIT</name>
        <address>RMT Briar Road, Twickenham - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: RMT Briar Road, Twickenham - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Rock Band<br>7. Genre: Rock<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: <br>10. Instruments: Piano/Keys, Guitar, Bass Guitar, Singing, Songwriting, Drum Kit<br>11. Other Tags: <br>12. Cost: £102 per term<br>13. About Opportunity: Saturday BandIt offers the opportunity to work alongside other musicians to create a set list of covers and original songs under the guidance of a BandIt tutor.  When ready, your band will be given the chance to join the RMT BandIt gig rota, which enables our bands to be considered for opportunities to get out into the community to perform at selected venues and festivals.<br><br>The above band slots are currently full, but we are looking to add two more sessions so please complete the form below and we’ll add you to the waiting list.  When we have enough students waiting who are of a similar age/ability to form an additional band, we’ll contact you.  In the meantime you might like to consider joining us on our holiday course, BandIt  <br>14. When: Saturdays, multiple dates between 9:00 - 13:00<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.richmondmusictrust.org.uk/site/ensembles/saturday-bandit/<br>16. Organisation Name: Richmond Music Trust<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
