            <value>The Fundamentals – led by Ky Osborne

This practical class is a fun, encouraging space, focusing on gaining confidence in improvisation, as well as covering some basic fundamental concepts within jazz theory and performance.</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
