          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>The Collective – led Shirley Tetteh

A project-led and creative development session run for and by female musicians aged 16+ offering a space for creating new compositions, exploring how jazz can work with other contemporary genres, and encouraging female musicians from all backgrounds to work collectively.</value>
