          <Data name="17. About Organisation">
            <value>Tomorrow’s Warriors invites young musicians interested in learning jazz and pursuing a career in music to join our Young Artist Development Programme.

We are looking for enthusiastic young musicians who are confident on their instruments to join our programme. Our sessions are completely free, so there’s no need to worry about the cost.

We run sessions every weekend during the school term and additional rehearsals throughout the week (see details below). To check if we can offer you a place, just fill in the details on the form below. Due to high demand we currently have a waiting list to join our programme, but we are still accepting musicians on certain instruments and are keen to accommodate for talented musicians.</value>
