        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: St.Paul's Way Trust School, Tower Hamlets - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Orchestra<br>7. Genre: Various<br>8. Age: 11 - 25<br>9. Level: Grade 5+<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: Contact for information<br>13. About Opportunity: The Tower Hamlets Youth Orchestra is in its sixth year. They play ambitious music in different styles, which provides the right level of challenge. Many members of this ensemble now take music lessons at different London Conservatoires. They are also taking the highest grade exams for their instrument. Some older members are studying music at University or College.<br>14. When: Contact for information<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://thames.towerhamlets.gov.uk/get-involved/join-a-group<br>16. Organisation Name: THAMES: Tower Hamlets Arts + Music Education Service<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
