        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: London - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Jazz Band<br>7. Genre: Jazz<br>8. Age: 15 - 25<br>9. Level: INvitation Only<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Invitation Only<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: Tomorrow’s Warriors has built a reputation as the hippest young jazz collective in the country and has long been acclaimed for spawning the most exciting young jazz musicians. Formed in September 2009, the young musicians of the Tomorrow’s Warriors Big Band who are generally aged between 15-25, have been honing their skills and creating a unique vibe and a shared fresh approach to jazz and contemporary music. Their speciality is performing not only big band arrangements of jazz standards but also hip new arrangements of their favourite contemporary tunes and new original works by our associated artists.<br><br>Tomorrow’s Warriors Big Band is always keen to engage in exciting artistic collaborations with other music, dance, poetry and literature, and visual arts groups, so do get in touch if you are interested in collaborating with us.<br>14. When: <br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://tomorrowswarriors.org/bands/tomorrows-warriors-big-band/<br>16. Organisation Name: Tomorrow's Warriors<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
