        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Walthamstow School for Girls - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Guitar Group<br>7. Genre: Rock<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: Beginners<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Preparatory<br>12. Cost: The fee for this group is separate to Music School Membership. Sign up at the link below.<br>13. About Opportunity: All the Young Dudes Guitar Group is for young guitarists who'd like to develop their skills and play rock and pop tunes with others. Members should have basic technique (be able to fret notes) or have started guitar lessons. Each term the group will perform in a concert to show off their fab new tunes.<br><br>How do I Join?<br>This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Debut Guitar Group' as the group you'd like to join.<br>14. When: Mondays 17:00 - 17:45<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.wfmusichub.org/groups/explore/youngdudes-guitar-group<br>16. Organisation Name: Waltham Forest Music Hub<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
