          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[All the Young Dudes Guitar Group is for young guitarists who'd like to develop their skills and play rock and pop tunes with others. Members should have basic technique (be able to fret notes) or have started guitar lessons. Each term the group will perform in a concert to show off their fab new tunes.

How do I Join?
This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Debut Guitar Group' as the group you'd like to join.]]></value>
