          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[This is open to any young person who is secondary aged and is interested in learning to produce their own music.

An music tech course for aspiring young producers, composers, song-writers, and MCs interested in creating their own beats and tracks.

Try your hand at working with a range of music production software (YuStudio, Logic, Ableton), experiment with electronic instruments or try recording vocals or live instruments using studio quality microphones.

How do I Join?
This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Beats and Bass' as the group you'd like to join.]]></value>
