      <Placemark>
        <name>Funk in the Forest</name>
        <address>Walthamstow School for Girls - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Walthamstow School for Girls - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Jazz Group<br>7. Genre: Jazz<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: Grade 3+<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Grade 3, Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: The fee for this group is separate to Music School Membership. Sign up at the link below.<br>13. About Opportunity: ‘Funk In The Forest’ are a classic jazz-funk combo consisting of front line instruments including trumpets, trombones, saxophones and clarinets, along with a rhythm section of pianos, guitars, bass and drums. Funk in the Forest is aimed at students who have achieved Grade 3 or above on their chosen instrument and gives them an opportunity to perform in the styles of Jazz, Funk, Rock and Soul along with developing more creative skills such as improvisation and composition. The ensemble rehearses weekly on Mondays during term time and works on performing a large array of music, from swing and bebop to more modern Funk and Soul.<br><br>How do I Join?<br>This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Funk in the Forest' as the group you'd like to join.<br>14. When: Mondays 18:30 - 19:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.wfmusichub.org/groups/explore/funk-in-the-forest<br>16. Organisation Name: Waltham Forest Music Hub<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1801-9C27B0-labelson</styleUrl>
