      <Placemark>
        <name>Junior Funksters</name>
        <address>Walthamstow School for Girls - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Walthamstow School for Girls - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Jazz Group<br>7. Genre: Jazz<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: Beginner to Grade 2<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Preparatory, Grade 1, Grade 2<br>12. Cost: The fee for this group is separate to Music School Membership. Sign up at the link below.<br>13. About Opportunity: ‘Junior Funksters’ perform a mixture of upbeat funk, modern pop tunes and classic jazz standards. The group is aimed at beginners up to grade 2/3 standard. All players of brass and woodwind instruments are welcome, along with anyone who wants to jam with the rhythm section - guitarists, bass players, pianists/keyboardists and drummers! The rehearsals cover everything from learning the basic skills needed to perform in a band to beginning to learn how to improvise on your chosen instrument, so come and join the jam!<br><br>How do I Join?<br>This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Junior Funksters' as the group you'd like to join.<br>14. When: Mondays 17:45 - 18:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.wfmusichub.org/groups/explore/junior-funksters<br>16. Organisation Name: Waltham Forest Music Hub<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
