        <name>Little Choir of Joy</name>
        <address>Walthamstow School for Girls - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Walthamstow School for Girls - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Choir<br>7. Genre: Choral<br>8. Age: 8 - 12<br>9. Level: Any<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: <br>12. Cost: Free (with music school membership)<br>13. About Opportunity: At the Choir of Joy children will learn lots of fun songs covering different styles including pop, folk and musical theatre. We’ll do fun warm ups, shake ourselves about and move to the beat. We’ll perform in concerts as soon as we can to share our uplifting music with others. We’re very proud that The Little Choir of Joy featured on the BBC Radio London Christmas Day Show as part of the Borough of Culture 2019.<br><br>This choir is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Little Choir of Joy' as the group you'd like to join.<br>14. When: Saturdays 11:45 - 12:45<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.wfmusichub.org/groups/explore/little-choir-of-joy<br>16. Organisation Name: Waltham Forest Music Hub<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
