        <name>Roll With It Guitar Group</name>
        <address>Walthamstow School for Girls - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: London<br>3. County: Greater London<br>4. Location: Walthamstow School for Girls - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Guitar Group<br>7. Genre: Rock<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: Musicians who can read some tab and play basic chords (Grade 1+)<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Grade 1, Grade 2, Grade 3, Grade 4, Grade 5, Grade 6, Grade 7, Grade 8<br>12. Cost: The fee for this group is separate to Music School Membership. Sign up at the link below.<br>13. About Opportunity: Roll With It Guitar Group is an exciting way to meet like-minded musicians with a passion for rock and pop music. Open to guitarists who play any type of guitar who can read some tab and play basic chords. This is a great opportunity to use skills in a real band situation. You will have the opportunity to pick your own songs and repertoire as well as the potential to write original material. Each term the group will perform in a concert to show off their fab new tunes.<br><br>How do I Join?<br>This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Improvers Guitar Group' as the group you'd like to join.<br>14. When: Mondays 17:00 - 17:45<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.wfmusichub.org/groups/explore/rollwithit-guitar-group<br>16. Organisation Name: Waltham Forest Music Hub<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
