          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[This is open to any young person who is secondary aged and is interested in writing their own songs.

From structure and tonality to genre and instrumentation, this course covers a whole range of skills that will be useful to any young person interested in creating their own music, particularly for GCSE composition.

All students need to bring along is themselves, any material they’ve written or started to write (don’t worry if they haven’t got any!) and an instrument (if portable).

How do I Join?
This group is part of the Music School - please sign up for Music School Groups and Ensembles and select 'Songwriter's Circle' as the group you'd like to join.]]></value>
