          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Wandsworth Jazz 2 is the feeder ensemble to the Wandsworth Jazz Orchestra. Jazz 2 is open to young musicians with a keen interest in jazz, playing Trumpet, Trombone, French Horn, Saxophone, Flute, Drums, Bass, Guitar and Keys at Grade 2 to Grade 5 standard.

The Jazz ensembles regularly perform at the Tooting Tram and Social and receive coaching from some of London’s top jazz musicians.

Jazz 2 rehearse on Saturday mornings, 10am-11am & 11am-11.50am.]]></value>
