          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>One of Wandsworth Music’s flagship ensembles, the Wandsworth Jazz Orchestra is for advanced musicians with a keen interest in Jazz and improvisation. The Orchestra performs a varied and challenging range of repertoire and performs annually at the London Jazz Festival alongside some of London’s top up and coming jazz talent.

Entrance is by audition for Grade 6/7+ musicians playing Trumpet, Trombone, French Horn, Saxophone, Drums, Bass, Guitar and Keys.

Wandsworth Jazz Orchestra rehearse on Wednesdays, 7.15pm-9pm.</value>
