          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>One of Wandsworth Music’s flagship ensembles, WPO is a full symphony orchestra for advanced orchestral musicians. The Orchestra performs a varied and challenging range of repertoire. Performance opportunities include concerts at the Royal Albert Hall, Fairfield Halls, Wimbledon Tennis Championships and an annual European tour. Recently the orchestra have visited Slovakia, Italy, Spain and Germany.

Entrance is by audition for Grade 6+ players of brass, wind, string and percussion instruments.

WPO rehearse on Saturdays, 10.45am-12.25pm. There are also 3 days of intensive sectional coaching during the Autumn and Spring Half Term holidays.</value>
