            <value>BEYOND is an inclusive, creative music ensemble for young people with Special Educational Needs/ Disabilities (SEND). The young musicians use a combination of traditional instruments, percussion, voices and music technology to create new music and develop their musical skills.

BEYOND rehearses twice a term at various schools in the borough, and perform at venues including The Royal Albert Hall and Fairfield Halls.</value>
