          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>For 1.5 Hours,
Receive £20

Each meeting will last 1.5 hours and each attendee will be paid £20.
Pizza,
Refreshments
And Chats

There will be pizza for those who want to stay for food and chats afterwards.
This is a paid opportunity for people who use our services to help shape them. 

We want to hear your voices to help shape our programmes for the future.
You must be age 16 or older to register and attend these sessions.
Become Part Of Our Programming Committee
Today!
We are currently recruiting for participants for our next Programming Committee Meeting. You must be over the age of 16 to attend.

Help choose new courses for our future programmes
Give us feedback on our current programmes
Tell us about your experiences with us and/or other programmes you take part in
Offer your ideas for new programmes, events or projects we could run
Meet and discuss your own experience with others on their own creative journey.</value>
