            <value>Audition</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>£75 - £125 per Term</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Join a great team of enthusiastic young musicians to enjoy making music of the highest standard with like-minded people. Membership is by audition only and open to anyone in full time education in Hampshire. Auditions will take place in early July so please apply now! We are in particular looking for Bassoons, Clarinets, Trumpets, Double Bass and Percussionists, but welcome all new applicants.  The deadline for applications is normally in June, but please contact us if you have missed the deadline and we will see what we can do. Places in the Hampshire County Youth Orchestra are limited and we do advise candidates to apply before the deadline. </value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Saturdays 10:30 - 15:30 (every 2 weeks)</value>
