          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>New players are welcome all year round, or just come along to have a try before committing to signing up.
Rehearsal Details

Day: Saturday (term time only)

Time: 9:30am

Venue: Fairfield Infant School

Grade: 4 +

Music is selected from a wide range of musical genres to suit players of approximately Grade 4 and upwards. Designed to provide a balance of challenge and support for all players, adaptations can be made to parts where needed, with personalised guidance and encouragement offered by our experienced directors.

Director: Steve Tanner and Lara Jelliff

Price: FREE - Voluntary contributions are welcome</value>
