        <address>Mayflower Studios, Southampton - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Hampshire<br>4. Location: Mayflower Studios, Southampton - UK<br>5. Type: Mentoring<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Professional Development<br>8. Age: 11 - 18<br>9. Level: any<br>10. Instruments: All<br>11. Other Tags: No Experience<br>12. Cost: <br>13. About Opportunity: Get mentoring and one-to-one support:<br>Aged 11–18 and want help to create and release music?<br><br>With music mentoring, you will get to work with a music expert to craft beats, write lyrics and produce tracks, as well as getting support to release and promote your own music!<br><br>Who is it for?<br><br>Singers, rappers, songwriters, producers and other musicians!<br><br>It doesn’t matter if you’re just starting out, not sure where to go next or have big ambitions - our team are here to help!<br><br>What is mentoring?<br><br>The opportunity to work with an expert mentor and take your next steps forward!<br><br>Try things out and get to know your mentor, then work together on what comes next including scheduling regular sessions at one of our recording studios:<br><br>Southampton — Mayflower Studios, City Center<br><br>IOW — The Basement, Ryde<br><br>Learn new skills, make new connections and work towards and smash your goals!<br>14. When: Sign Up<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.siowmusic.org/music-mentoring<br>16. Organisation Name: SIOW Music<br>17. About Organisation: The new home for Southampton Music Hub, IOW Music Hub and Southampton Music Services<br><br>Empowering children and young people to make, learn and love music<br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.siowmusic.org<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
