          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Get mentoring and one-to-one support:
Aged 11–18 and want help to create and release music?

With music mentoring, you will get to work with a music expert to craft beats, write lyrics and produce tracks, as well as getting support to release and promote your own music!

Who is it for?

Singers, rappers, songwriters, producers and other musicians!

It doesn’t matter if you’re just starting out, not sure where to go next or have big ambitions - our team are here to help!

What is mentoring?

The opportunity to work with an expert mentor and take your next steps forward!

Try things out and get to know your mentor, then work together on what comes next including scheduling regular sessions at one of our recording studios:

Southampton — Mayflower Studios, City Center

IOW — The Basement, Ryde

Learn new skills, make new connections and work towards and smash your goals!</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Sign Up</value>
          </Data>
