      <Placemark>
        <name>Playback</name>
        <address>the Base Guildhall - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Hampshire<br>4. Location: the Base Guildhall - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Production/Mixing<br>8. Age: 18 +<br>9. Level: all Abilities<br>10. Instruments: Songwriting, Producing, Composing<br>11. Other Tags: Free, No Experience<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: A night to show off your work-in-progress tracks.<br> <br>PLAYBACK is an evening to test out your latest track, give and receive feedback and meet new people. Whether you just need advice on the ending, the mix, or the lyrics, or if it’s a rough idea and you don’t know where to take it…  Meet with like-minded musicians and receive constructive feedback on how to take your music to the next level, and share your knowledge in return.<br>Just get in touch with us via hello@thebaseguildhall.com or our Instagram, and send us your track (a soundcloud link/google drive is best), or bring it on the night. Let us know what kind of feedback you want, and what you don’t! Feedback will be friendly and constructive from the group, and then, even better, talk to people afterwards, and get into the weeds of snare selection and panning.<br> <br>The evening is hosted by The BASE Guildhall and Liam Quinn. Liam is a composer and sound designer working music for media with 15 years of experience.<br>14. When: Various Dates<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://thebaseguildhall.com/booking/<br>16. Organisation Name: The BASE - Guildhall<br>17. About Organisation: The basement of Portsmouth Guildhall has been transformed into an exciting, new creative space where 11-25 year olds can meet and explore their creative potential!<br><br>The BASE gives young people access to:<br><br>BAND REHEARSAL ROOM WITH BACKLINE EQUIPMENT<br>DJ MIXING SPACE<br>LARGE AV SUITE WITH ACCESS TO SPECIALIST SOFTWARE<br>SMALL PERFORMANCE SPACE<br>LOUNGE/CHILL OUT SPACE<br>EXHIBITION AREA<br>18. Organisation Website: https://thebaseguildhall.com<br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: Free membership required (only PO postcode eligible)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1637-FFD600-labelson</styleUrl>
