        <address>the Base Guildhall - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Hampshire<br>4. Location: the Base Guildhall - UK<br>5. Type: Mentoring<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Various<br>8. Age: 11 - 30<br>9. Level: all abilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Free, No Experience<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: Thinking about a creative future? Whatever your dreams are, Your BASEplan is set up to advocate and support your future in the creative and cultural industries.<br><br>Maybe you already know what you want to do creatively; but are unsure how to begin? Or you have already begun; but are not sure what comes next? <br><br>No matter what stage you are at Your BASEplan is a flexible drop-in opportunity for any young person aged 11-30. Come to The Base Guildhall and find the support of creative professionals, to work through your aspirations in search of practical plans.<br><br>Sessions will offer you scope to:<br><br>Talk through your ideas and goals<br>Ask and answer your questions about creative careers<br>Understand what creative careers really look like<br>Advance in an area you are already developing<br>Get advice from someone who’s working in the industry<br>Start/continue shaping your own path with professional guidance<br>14. When: Wednesday Afternoons<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://thebaseguildhall.com/booking/<br>16. Organisation Name: The BASE - Guildhall<br>17. About Organisation: The basement of Portsmouth Guildhall has been transformed into an exciting, new creative space where 11-25 year olds can meet and explore their creative potential!<br><br>The BASE gives young people access to:<br><br>BAND REHEARSAL ROOM WITH BACKLINE EQUIPMENT<br>DJ MIXING SPACE<br>LARGE AV SUITE WITH ACCESS TO SPECIALIST SOFTWARE<br>SMALL PERFORMANCE SPACE<br>LOUNGE/CHILL OUT SPACE<br>EXHIBITION AREA<br>18. Organisation Website: https://thebaseguildhall.com<br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: Free membership required (only PO postcode eligible)]]></description>
