          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Thinking about a creative future? Whatever your dreams are, Your BASEplan is set up to advocate and support your future in the creative and cultural industries.

Maybe you already know what you want to do creatively; but are unsure how to begin? Or you have already begun; but are not sure what comes next? 

No matter what stage you are at Your BASEplan is a flexible drop-in opportunity for any young person aged 11-30. Come to The Base Guildhall and find the support of creative professionals, to work through your aspirations in search of practical plans.

Sessions will offer you scope to:

Talk through your ideas and goals
Ask and answer your questions about creative careers
Understand what creative careers really look like
Advance in an area you are already developing
Get advice from someone who’s working in the industry
Start/continue shaping your own path with professional guidance</value>
          </Data>
