      <Placemark>
        <name>Girls Make Music</name>
        <address>Mayflower Studios, Southampton - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Hampshire<br>4. Location: Mayflower Studios, Southampton - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Production/Mixing<br>8. Age: 11 - 18 (or 21?)<br>9. Level: all abilities<br>10. Instruments: Producing, Songwriting<br>11. Other Tags: Women/Non-Binary, Free<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: Girls Make Music - a 2 day short course in Music Production - for girls aged 13-18!<br><br>In this course, we will explore:<br><br>Music Production<br><br>Songwriting<br><br>Recording<br><br>Using BandLab & other music production software!<br><br>We encourage exploration and collaboration with each other, fostering diversity and inclusion in our sessions.<br><br>Whether you are just starting out on your musical journey or you’re well on your way, the club is open to all regardless of your musical experience.<br><br>This is a course that will take place over 2 days at our Music Studio in Mayflower Studios. <br><br>If there is a high amount of demand for spaces on the 2 day course, we may instead offer everyone a 1 day course that will take place on the 8th and 9th, to enable more people to attend and get the support they need!<br>14. When: 8th - 9th April (10:00 - 15:00)<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.siowmusic.org/girlsmakemusic<br>16. Organisation Name: SIOW Music<br>17. About Organisation: The new home for Southampton Music Hub, IOW Music Hub and Southampton Music Services<br><br>Empowering children and young people to make, learn and love music<br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.siowmusic.org<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1637-FFD600-labelson</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
