            <value>Free</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[Girls Make Music - a 2 day short course in Music Production - for girls aged 13-18!

In this course, we will explore:

Music Production

Songwriting

Recording

Using BandLab & other music production software!

We encourage exploration and collaboration with each other, fostering diversity and inclusion in our sessions.

Whether you are just starting out on your musical journey or you’re well on your way, the club is open to all regardless of your musical experience.

This is a course that will take place over 2 days at our Music Studio in Mayflower Studios. 

If there is a high amount of demand for spaces on the 2 day course, we may instead offer everyone a 1 day course that will take place on the 8th and 9th, to enable more people to attend and get the support they need!]]></value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>8th - 9th April (10:00 - 15:00)</value>
          </Data>
