          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Horn Club is open to all horn players of grade 5 and above.

The Horn Club will primarily focus on performing ensemble music, providing your child with valuable stage experience and opportunities to showcase their talent as well as having fun along the way.

Our young horn players will have the chance to learn the core orchestral repertoire, transposition techniques, and how to play effectively as part of an orchestral horn section.

Horn Club is open to all Oxfordshire French Horn students of grade 5, including those privately taught.</value>
