          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>£8.20 per session</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>We invite all young people who love singing to join Oxfordshire’s County Youth Choir. We are open to both boys and girls and cater for soprano, alto, tenor and bass voice parts. No audition is necessary, but being able to read music would be a distinct advantage.

Oxfordshire County Youth Choir enjoys singing in a variety of styles and aims to perform at the end of each term. There are also opportunities to sing with some of the county’s instrumental ensembles.

Come along on a Thursday and see if you like it!</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Thursdays 18:30 - 20:00</value>
          </Data>
