      <Placemark>
        <name>Oxfordshire Youth Music Theatre</name>
        <address>Centre for Music, Bayswater Road, Headington - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Oxfordshire<br>4. Location: Centre for Music, Bayswater Road, Headington - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Musical Theatre Group<br>7. Genre: Musical Theatre<br>8. Age: 12 - 18<br>9. Level: audtioned<br>10. Instruments: Singing<br>11. Other Tags: Audition<br>12. Cost: £500 across the year<br>13. About Opportunity: A teenage musical theatre group based in Oxford, producing one show per year, alternating between the Oxford Playhouse and another Oxford Theatre.<br><br>Singers, dancers and actors from the Oxfordshire Youth Music Theatre are a group of talented 12 to 18-year-olds from across the county.<br><br>Over the last few years OYMT has built a reputation of presenting high quality youth theatre, with many former members now enjoying successful professional careers in West End hits such as Rock of Ages and Wicked, and even the 25th and 30th anniversary performances of Les Misérables.<br><br>The last show was Cats, which took place at the Centre for Music from 2 to 4 April 2025. The company is looking for new members for the next season, when we hope to stage a production of Les Misérables in a professional theatre. <br><br>Standards<br><br>We aim to encourage the highest standards in music theatre. We work as a company during the rehearsal period with professional directors, set and lighting designers.<br><br>We are also keen to hear from students interested in any aspects of stage management.<br>14. When: Monday evenings, 6.45pm – 9.15pm and one Saturday afternoon per month, 1.30pm - 5.30pm<br><br><br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/residents/music-service/music-groups/choirs-and-performing-arts/youth-music-theatre<br>16. Organisation Name: Oxfordshire Music Service<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/residents/music-service<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1801-9C27B0-labelson</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="2. Region">
            <value>South East</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="3. County">
            <value>Oxfordshire</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="4. Location">
            <value>Centre for Music, Bayswater Road, Headington - UK</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="5. Type">
            <value>Ensemble</value>
