      <Placemark>
        <name>Rockschool</name>
        <address>Centre for Music, Bayswater Road, Headington - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Oxfordshire<br>4. Location: Centre for Music, Bayswater Road, Headington - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Rock<br>8. Age: 11 - 18<br>9. Level: all abilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: <br>12. Cost: £8.20 per session<br>13. About Opportunity: The UK’s first digital JamPod is a new way to learn. Play electric guitar, bass guitar, drums, keyboards or sing, using cutting-edge technology to enable composing, playing and recording in a silent studio environment.<br><br>Come and join a band, or bring some friends and form your own band. Compose, perform and record your own songs (or cover versions) with expert tuition in the high-tech setting of the JamPod Academy.<br><br><br>14. When: Tuesdays 19:00 - 20:30<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/residents/music-service/music-groups/rockschool<br>16. Organisation Name: Oxfordshire Music Service<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/residents/music-service<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
