          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>The UK’s first digital JamPod is a new way to learn. Play electric guitar, bass guitar, drums, keyboards or sing, using cutting-edge technology to enable composing, playing and recording in a silent studio environment.

Come and join a band, or bring some friends and form your own band. Compose, perform and record your own songs (or cover versions) with expert tuition in the high-tech setting of the JamPod Academy.

</value>
