      <Placemark>
        <name>Oxfordshire Intermediate Orchestra</name>
        <address>Executive Lounge, Didcot Town Football Club, Didcot - UK</address>
        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Oxfordshire<br>4. Location: Executive Lounge, Didcot Town Football Club, Didcot - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Orchestral<br>8. Age: <br>9. Level: grade 2  - 4<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Grade 2, Grade 3, Grade 4<br>12. Cost: £28 per session<br>13. About Opportunity: The orchestra will explore a range of repertoire with highly experienced tutors who are keen to encourage and help your child to improve their sight-reading, ensemble and social skills. In previous years, music has included Disney favourites, famous classics such as Dvorak's New World Symphony, as well as a commissioned piece written especially for OIO! These were performed in a fantastic end-of-year concert alongside the County's top orchestras at the prestigious Dorchester Abbey. We hope to do something similar next year to showcase the fantastic talent we have in Oxfordshire together in our 100 strong orchestra!<br>14. When: Various dates (check website for more details)<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/residents/music-service/music-groups/orchestras/oio<br>16. Organisation Name: Oxfordshire Music Service<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: https://www.oxfordshire.gov.uk/residents/music-service<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
