          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Introduction to music for young children

Delivered by a qualified music and strings teacher, these classes aim to develop a love and understanding of music for young children aged 2 to 7 years. 

They will be introduced to musical appreciation, notation, pitch training and violins through a fun and engaging approach suitable for their age, including the use of balls, parachute, violins, percussion instruments, puppets, story songs and a lot more. </value>
