        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South West<br>3. County: Somerset<br>4. Location: The Key Centre, Feltham Lane, Frome, BA11 5AJ - UK<br>5. Type: Workshop<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): <br>7. Genre: Early Years<br>8. Age: Under 2<br>9. Level: All ABilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Early Years, Free<br>12. Cost: <br>13. About Opportunity: Join us in Frome for Dads Rock – a regular music-making session for dads or male caregivers and children under 5!<br><br>Unleash your child’s potential with music! Develop emotional control, language, math skills & creativity through play.<br><br>Discover how child-led musical play helps with developing baby and toddler’s managing big emotions, powerful communication skills, a love of language, a foundation in numbers and their inner rockstar.<br><br>Dads Rock (it’s not just a saying, it’s a movement!) is also a chance to build a community with other Dads and share your parenting adventure and musical experiences.<br><br>VENUE: The Key Centre, Feltham Lane, Frome, BA11 5AJ<br><br>FREQUENCY: Session dates are Saturday mornings 10am – 11.30am<br><br>17th January<br>31st January<br>28th February<br>14th March<br>28th March<br>BOOKING INFO: https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/frome-dads-rock-2026-tickets-1978359255790?aff=oddtdtcreator<br>14. When: Saturdays 10:00 - 11:30 <br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://evolvemusic.org.uk/whats-on/month/<br>16. Organisation Name: Evolve Music<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
