            <value>Piccolo/Flute, Clarinet, Oboe, Cor Anglais, Bassoon, Trumpet, Trombone, Tuba, Horns, Harp, Violin, Viola, Cello, Double Bass, Percussion, Piano/Keys, Singing, Euphonium, Saxophone, Recorder</value>
