          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Piano Tuition School

A typical classical tuition schools workshop provides a 1-2-1 masterclass style session with one of our professional piano specialists, along with small ensemble group activities throughout the day.

Each workshop ends with an informal showcase performance for family and friends.

Piano Tuition School Workshop dates for 2025-26 to be announced soon
Find out more about our professional tutor team here:

HELEN REID
ANDREW TREWHELLA
KIMON PALIKAROPOULOS
A piano student sat at a piano with a tutor in one of our classical tuition school workshops
Strings Tuition School

A typical classical tuition schools workshop provides a 1-2-1 masterclass style session with one of our professional piano specialists, along with small ensemble group activities throughout the day. Sometimes we link with the Wind Tuition School to form mixed chamber ensemble work.

Each workshop ends with an informal showcase performance for family and friends.

Strings Tuition School Workshop dates for 2025-26 to be announced soon
Find out more about our professional tutor here:

CHRIS SAMPSON
A cello student performing in a masterclass session
