          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Designed for musicians in Key Stage 4 upwards, our Music Production activities provide opportunities for students who are new to working with production software and recording, as well as more experienced producers looking to develop their skills further. Whether you are focussed on improving your use of Digital Audio Workstations or wanting to finesse your tracks, we are here to help!

We offer a varied range of activities to suit your skills levels, needs, time, and budget.

Find out more about our music production tutor below:

MATTHEW KER

Please note that we can sometimes offer a means-tested grant to cover the cost of our activities.
Use the Contact Form at the bottom of this page to get in touch today</value>
