          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Adults, come and play @ FMD on Tuesdays at 9.30 am

This is a 40 minute session for all adults who would like to start playing their instrument again.

It really doesn’t matter if you think you might have forgotten how to play; we play a variety of styles of music that suit the playing ability of everyone who joins us.

All orchestral instruments are welcome.

Give it a go, you might even enjoy it!</value>
