        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: Surrey<br>4. Location: Christ's College, Larch Avenue, Guildford - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Orchestra<br>7. Genre: Orchestral<br>8. Age: Young People 12+<br>9. Level: All abilities<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: Free<br>12. Cost: Free<br>13. About Opportunity: Unlimited Potential (UP!) Orchestra is an inclusive ensemble for young people aged 12 and above with no audition required and all abilities welcome.<br><br>The group meets every other Saturday and provides a supportive space for making music, learning new instruments, developing confidence, and collaborating with others. Sessions are led by specialist tutors who support a wide range of needs and interests.<br>14. When: Saturday 10:30 - 12:30 (every 2 weeks)<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.surreycc.gov.uk/culture-and-leisure/arts/music/ensembles/up<br>16. Organisation Name: Surrey Arts<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: <br>19. Only for London/Local?: Local Only<br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
