          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Unlimited Potential (UP!) Orchestra is an inclusive ensemble for young people aged 12 and above with no audition required and all abilities welcome.

The group meets every other Saturday and provides a supportive space for making music, learning new instruments, developing confidence, and collaborating with others. Sessions are led by specialist tutors who support a wide range of needs and interests.</value>
