          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Held ONLINE
If you’re a musician, there are lots of different aspects to your career that you must juggle — being your own social media manager, dealing with contracts and finances, project managing your releases and tours, and so much more. 

Sometimes it’s difficult to know where to start, and that’s where our Business Skills workshops come in. These online sessions offer advice and guidance on a wide range of topics to help you manage the many different parts of being a musician with confidence. They are free to join, and led by experts who can give you the tools you need to build a sustainable career in music. 

Upcoming sessions will appear below. </value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Multiple - see opportunity page for details</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
