          <Data name="9. Level">
            <value>Be a working musician who has made at least 40% of your income from music over the past two years. Musicians with a long-term health condition and/​or disability that impacts their ability to work as a musician will just need to show some income from music within the past 2 years.</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="10. Instruments">
            <value>All</value>
