          <Data name="12. Cost">
            <value>Free</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>Open up your world when you join The National Youth Orchestra. Take on new 
ideas, meet new friends, visit new places and explore music like never before.  
You will join a nationwide community of musicians who are just as passionate as 
you about orchestral music. You will experience every second of this musical 
adventure with them by your side, playing your part in shaping a welcoming 
environment for everyone to thrive.  
You will reach new heights as a musician through coaching from NYO’s world
class musical and support teams. This will give you the confidence to conquer 
huge musical challenges.   
Play massive orchestral masterworks and stunning ensemble music, whilst 
exploring new musical concepts and the work of a diverse range of composers.   
You will perform with and for teenagers across the UK. With the guidance of 
leading creative innovators, you’ll find new ways to perform and present the music 
you love, in concert halls, schools and surprising spaces and places.</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Annually</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
            <value>https://www.nyo.org.uk/get-involved/the-nyo-orchestra</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="16. Organisation Name">
            <value>National Youth Orchestra</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="17. About Organisation">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="18. Organisation Website">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="19. Only for London/Local?">
            <value>No Restriction</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="20. Extra Notes">
            <value/>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
