          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value><![CDATA[West Sussex Youth Orchestra sits at the pinnacle of the progression of string orchestras & wind bands offered by West Sussex Music. Performances include the finals of the Music for Youth National Festival at Symphony Hall, Birmingham, and venues across West Sussex and toured Europe.

Current repertoire includes:

Brahms Academic Festival Overture
Elgar Pomp and Circumstance
Schubert Unfinished Symphony
Stravinsky – Firebird
Patrick Doyle & John Williams – Harry Potter
Tchaikovsky – Swan Lake]]></value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="14. When">
            <value>Saturdays (Term Time)</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="15. Opportunity Website / Signup">
            <value/>
          </Data>
