            <value>West Sussex Music</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="17. About Organisation">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="18. Organisation Website">
            <value>https://westsussexmusic.co.uk</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="19. Only for London/Local?">
            <value/>
          </Data>
          <Data name="20. Extra Notes">
            <value>Who can join?  Grade 5 and above, by audition
(Please note: Members of WSYO are also expected to be part of our West Sussex Youth String/Wind Orchestras)

When does the orchestra take place? Rehearsals take place on Saturdays during term-time at Horsham Music Centre, c/o Millais School, Depot Road, RH13 5HR

How do I apply to join West Sussex Youth Orchestra? Click the button below to apply, and we will get in touch with you to arrange an audition
</value>
