          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>West Sussex Youth Choir

West Sussex Youth Choir is a mixed-voice choir for experienced singers aged 13yrs to 21yrs. We learn large-scale choral works, with opportunities to perform with an orchestra, as well as lighter and more contemporary repertoire.

An ability to read music isn’t essential and sessions offer a chance for singers to build their skills and confidence with a focus on having fun and being creative. Singers with changing voices are supported during rehearsals as they find their new tenor and bass registers.

Who can join?  Anyone aged 13yrs to 21yrs with a passion for singing.
Apply now and try something new!

When does the choir take place? Rehearsals take place on Saturdays, 9am – 10:30am at Horsham Music Centre, c/o Millais School, RH13 5HR</value>
