          <Data name="13. About Opportunity">
            <value>
West Sussex Junior Orchestras – An exciting ensemble experience for elementary young musicians!

Our Junior Orchestras are the perfect platform for aspiring musicians to come together to explore the joy of making music in a fun and supportive environment and offer the chance to develop orchestral skills, build confidence, and make new friends.

The Junior Orchestras rehearse weekly at their local Music Centre, coming together at the end of every term for a combined performance at concert venues across West Sussex.

Junior Orchestra is suitable for learners of orchestral instruments from elementary level up to Stage 1 (Grade 1).
This exciting ensemble programme is available at Bognor Regis, Chichester, Horsham and Worthing Music Centres.</value>
          </Data>
