        <description><![CDATA[2. Region: South East<br>3. County: West Sussex<br>4. Location: Mallais School, Horsham - UK<br>5. Type: Ensemble<br>6. Ensemble (if app.): Percussion Ensemble<br>7. Genre: Various<br>8. Age: 7 - 13<br>9. Level: Any Ability<br>10. Instruments: <br>11. Other Tags: No Experience<br>12. Cost: From £78 per term<br>13. About Opportunity: For complete beginner to intermediate percussion players<br><br>We’re thrilled to introduce our percussion group: Drum Lab!<br><br>Drum Lab offers students a new musical experience, providing an opportunity for the many young students who want to play drums/percussion instruments in a fun, safe, and exciting group. Playing all styles of music on a wide variety of instruments, this is the perfect group for all budding young drummers, no experience necessary!<br><br>Who can join? Anyone in school years 3-8 (age 7-13)<br><br>Where can I join? Drum Lab meets at three different venues at our music centres. Apply now and try something new!<br>14. When: Saturdays 12:00 - 13:00<br>15. Opportunity Website / Signup: https://www.westsussexmusic.co.uk/horsham-music-centre/<br>16. Organisation Name: West Sussex Music<br>17. About Organisation: <br>18. Organisation Website: https://westsussexmusic.co.uk<br>19. Only for London/Local?: <br>20. Extra Notes: ]]></description>
